                                                <p>Kim began working at Johnny's in 2019 in the Customer Care
                                                    Department, joined the Commercial Sales Team in 2020 as a Sales
                                                    Support Specialist, and has quickly advanced to the role of
                                                    Territory Sales Representative for the Central U.S.</p>
                                                <p>Originally from Oklahoma, Kim spent 20 years in Dallas, Texas before
                                                    moving to Maine with her husband in 2013, seeking a change of pace,
                                                    less concrete, and more woods.</p>
                                                <p>Kim gained experience in the agriculture industry by working for two
