                                                        <span class="qmark">&ldquo;&nbsp;</span>As a farmer myself, I
                                                        understand the goals and frustrations of commercial agriculture.
                                                        Your success is my priority! I want to be a partner you can rely
                                                        on for the information, seed, and supplies you need to continue
