                                                    </div>
                                                    <div class="repquote"
                                                        style="font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.5em; font-style: italic;">
                                                        <span class="qmark">&ldquo;&nbsp;</span>Working in my garden and
                                                        growing my own food is one of my greatest pleasures in life. I
                                                        am proud to be involved in the business of agriculture, and look
                                                        forward to learning from and with the growers in my territory
                                                        and assisting with their needs in any way that I can.<span
                                                            class="qmark">&nbsp;&rdquo;</span>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
                                                <p>Amy brings to the team a wealth of experience and working familiarity
                                                    with Johnny's varieties from having fulfilled a series of roles
                                                    within our Contact Center and the Albion Research &amp; Trialing
                                                    Farm. While at Johnny's Research Farm, she acquired hands-on
                                                    experience spanning our entire seed-production process &mdash; from
                                                    starting crops in the greenhouse, transplanting, and cultivating to
                                                    harvesting, sluicing, and cleaning seeds. This past experience has
                                                    given her insight into and appreciation for crops not only for the
                                                    edible harvest they provide, but also for their seed potential.</p>
                                                <p>Amy possesses deep working knowledge accrued by running her own
                                                    homestead farm, as well. With the goal of meeting her family's needs
                                                    to every extent possible, she engages in year-round production of
                                                    vegetables, fruit, and free-range livestock. She looks forward to
                                                    connecting with commercial growers throughout her territory.</p>
